        "rich_text_CTP944": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The Portuguese Cut Diamond vs Round Brilliant comparison reveals a clear distinction: while the Round Brilliant prioritizes balance and uniformity, the Portuguese Cut celebrates depth and individuality. For those who appreciate rare craftsmanship and vintage allure, the Portuguese Cut offers a touch of exclusivity unmatched by mass-market designs.</p><p>Explore this brilliance redefined — discover Lucira’s handcrafted<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond</span></a> cuts that reflect both tradition and innovation.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9YdFx4": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lab-Grown Portuguese Cut Diamonds: The Perfect Blend of Ethics and Excellence",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Lab-Grown Portuguese Cut Diamonds: The Perfect Blend of Ethics and Excellence</h2><p>Lucira Jewelry’s Lab Grown Portuguese Cut Diamonds represent the future of fine jewelry combining advanced technology with artistic heritage. By cultivating diamonds in controlled laboratory environments, we recreate the same physical, chemical, and optical properties of natural diamonds without the environmental cost of mining.</p>",
            "custom_id": "labgrown"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_n9ACQy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Benefits of Lab Grown Portuguese Cut Diamonds",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Benefits of Lab Grown Portuguese Cut Diamonds</h3>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_iCfqX7": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Benefit.jpg",
            "text": "<ul><li>Zero mining impact: Each diamond is grown ethically, without disturbing ecosystems.<br/></li><li>Certified quality: Every Lucira diamond is IGI-certified, ensuring authenticity and transparency.<br/></li><li>Accessible luxury: Lab grown diamonds provide exceptional brilliance at a fraction of the traditional price.<br/></li></ul><p>This evolution allows you to own a piece of timeless beauty — responsibly created and ethically sourced.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_7jByCU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Portuguese Cut Diamond Ring: Vintage Charm With Modern Design",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Portuguese Cut Diamond Ring: Vintage Charm With Modern Design</h2><p>A Portuguese Cut Diamond Ring is more than jewelry; it is a statement of sophistication. Lucira Jewelry combines the vintage artistry of the Portuguese Cut with contemporary design sensibilities.</p><p>Whether it’s a classic solitaire, a delicate halo, or an elegant side-stone setting, the Portuguese Cut’s deep brilliance enhances every design. Each ring, including<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/couple-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> couple rings</span></a>, is handcrafted to reflect individuality — perfect for engagements, anniversaries, or meaningful milestones.</p><p>At Lucira, our rings are not just worn; they’re experienced — created with precision, passion, and purpose.</p>",
            "custom_id": "ring"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Choose Your Portuguese Diamond Cut",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Choose Your Portuguese Diamond Cut</h2><h3>Cut Precision</h3><p>Choose a diamond with precise symmetry and proportion. The intricate faceting demands expert craftsmanship for maximum light performance.</p><h3>Carat and Proportion</h3><p>The depth of the Portuguese Cut may slightly reduce surface area, so balance carat weight with proportion for optimal brilliance.</p><h3>Metal Setting</h3><p>Platinum and white gold settings complement the diamond’s reflective geometry, while yellow gold offers a warm, vintage contrast.</p><h3>Certification & Trust</h3><p>Every Lucira diamond comes with an IGI Certification, ensuring quality and traceability. To explore your perfect stone, book a virtual consultation with our jewelry specialists.</p>",
            "custom_id": "choose"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_dLp73f": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Caring for Your Portuguese Cut Diamond",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Caring for Your Portuguese Cut Diamond</h2>",
            "custom_id": "care"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_jMJx93": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Jewelry_Tip_Care_6d1ee305-bb10-4585-b6c2-5be2dd7d18dc.jpg",
            "text": "<p>To maintain the brilliance of your Portuguese Cut Diamond, regular care is essential:</p><ul><li>Clean gently using mild soap and warm water.<br/></li><li>Avoid harsh chemicals that may dull the facets.<br/></li><li>Schedule professional cleaning through Lucira’s Lifetime Exchange and Care Program.<br/></li></ul><p>With thoughtful care, your diamond will remain as radiant as the day it was created.</p>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_YxXCc9": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Future of the Portuguese Cut",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Future of the Portuguese Cut</h2><p>The global jewelry landscape is undergoing a remarkable transformation. Today’s conscious consumers seek more than just beauty — they desire pieces that embody their values as well as their style. The lab-grown Portuguese Cut Diamond perfectly captures this shift, blending sustainability with timeless sophistication.</p><p>At Lucira Jewelry, we are redefining what luxury means. Each piece we create carries a story of purpose, progress, and purity. The Portuguese Cut is not just a nod to the past; it is a vision for the future — where every facet shines with integrity.</p>",
            "custom_id": "future"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_kiLweW": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion: A Legacy of Light",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion: A Legacy of Light</h2><p>The Portuguese Cut Diamond stands as a symbol of brilliance, artistry, and ethics — a perfect harmony of history and innovation. For those who seek a diamond as rare as their love, Lucira Jewelry offers creations that embody both conscience and craftsmanship.</p><p>Design your own<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-rings\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> lab grown diamond rings</span></a> today. Book a free virtual consultation or visit our Experience Store to bring your dream ring to life — where brilliance meets responsibility.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion"
          }
        }
      },
